headline: CF Industries Holdings, Inc. Declares Quarterly Dividend and Confirms Dates for First Quarter 2025 Results and Conference Call
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., April 29, 2025--CF Industries Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: CF) today reported that its board of directors has declared a $0.50 per share dividend on its common stock. The dividend will be payable on May 30, 2025, to stockholders of record as of May 15, 2025.

headline: Smurfit Westrock is Set to Report Q1 Earnings: Here's What to Expect
summary: SW's Q1 results are likely to reflect packaging demand for food, beverages and medicines, and growth in e-commerce activities, offset by higher costs.
